  <acronym>PITCH</acronym>
  <official_title>A Randomized , Open Label, Dose Titration Study to Evaluate the Effect of Pitavastatin Versus Atorvastatin in Patients With Hypercholesterolemia and Mild to Moderate Hepatic Damage</official_title>
