  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Statin is an effective drug to treat hyperlipidemia (hypercholesterolemia), and it rarely
      leads to hepatic damage to the patients with hepatic disorder. For these patients, intensive
      monitoring is required.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
